     </blockquote> 
     <cite><span>Kurt Svoboda</span><br> Senior Assistant Athletic Director, Stanford University</cite> 
    </div> 
   </div> 
  </section> 
  <section> 
   <div class="container"> 
    <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-2"> 
     <h3>One tagboard, many faces</h3> 
     <p>The Tagboard platform is centralized but is designed for multiple, simultaneous displays, whether mobile or projected, tagboard.com or yourdomain.com.</p> 
    </div> 
    <div class="col-sm-4"> 
     <img src="https://static.tagboard.com/public/img/aboutus_responsive.svg?eff2248b" alt="" class="img-responsive" style="margin: 0 auto; max-height: 164px;"> 
    </div> 
   </div> 
  </section> 
  <section> 
   <div class="container"> 
    <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-2"> 
     <img src="https://static.tagboard.com/public/img/aboutus_upgradepro.svg?95c8a537" alt="" class="img-responsive" style="margin: 0 auto; height: 220px;"> 
    </div> 
    <div class="col-sm-4"> 
     <h3>Go <strong>Pro</strong>, get more</h3> 
     <p>Tagboards come with everything you need to host the social conversation, but if you need more, we offer Pro accounts that give you enhanced features like more tagboards, and elevated post limits.</p> 
     <a href="https://about.tagboard.com/pro" class="btn btn-primary">Request a Tagboard Pro account</a> 
    </div> 
   </div> 
  </section> 
